snippet.title: U.S. Department of State
snippet.description:
Welcome to the official U.S. Department of State YouTube channel. The Department of State leads America’s foreign policy through diplomacy, advocacy, and assistance by advancing the interests of the American people, their safety, and economic prosperity. It is our vision to promote and demonstrate democratic values and advance a free, peaceful, and prosperous world on behalf of the American people.

Here you will find original video content produced by the State Department including, remarks by the Secretary of State, Department press briefings, broadcast video coverage of current events, special video collections based on foreign policy issues, and conversations with U.S. diplomats and foreign affairs professionals. Subscribe to our channel for up-to-date news on the work of the U.S. Department of State.
